<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ العِدَدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- لَا عِدَّةَ فِي فُرْقَةِ حَيٍّ قَبْلَ وَطْءٍ وَخَلْوَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ لِوَطْءٍ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- كَوْنُهَا يُوطَأُ مِثْلُهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَكَوْنُهُ يَلْحَقُ بِهِ الوَلَدُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلِخَلْوَةٍ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- مُطَاوَعَتُهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَعِلْمُهُ بِهَا، وَلَوْ مَعَ مَانِعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَتَلْزَمُ لِوَفَاةٍ مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالمُعْتَدَّاتُ سِتٌّ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> الحَامِلُ: وَعِدَّتُهَا مُطْلَقاً إِلَى وَضْعِ كُلِّ حَمْلٍ تَصِيرُ بِهِ أَمَةٌ أُمَّ وَلَدٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ:</span> لُحُوقُهُ لِلزَّوْجِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَقَلُّ مُدَّتِهِ:</span> سِتَّةُ أَشْهُرٍ،<span class="c5"> وَغَالِبُهَا:</span> تِسْعَةٌ،<span class="c5"> وَأَكْثَرُهَا:</span> أَرْبَعُ سِنِينَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَيُبَاحُ إِلْقَاءُ نُطْفَةٍ قَبْلَ أَرْبَعِينَ يَوْماً بِدَوَاءٍ مُبَاحٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ب) و (د): مطاوعته.</p> </div>